  "text": "I am wrong. Firstly, we would suggest that possibility, probability vortices include those in which the entity known as Gandalf has a lengthier incarnation. Secondly, we would suggest that this entity goes to a graduation if it desires otherwise it may choose to reincarnate, to be with those companions it has loved. Thirdly, the entity known to you as Betty has the means of making the entity more distorted towards comfort, discomfort.",
